                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.672/133: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Special Mission at Lausanne</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lausanne</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-07-25T14:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 25, 1923—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 25—1:23 pan.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>556. Following is translation of statement which appeared in the Swiss press
                    today obviously given out by the Turkish delegation.</p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>“The United States of North America have not signed the treaty of peace,
                        having entered into separate negotiations with the Turks with a view to
                        concluding a Turco-American treaty of peace.</p>
                    <p>Certain difficulties have arisen, principally concerning the rights of
                        American citizens in Turkey. The United States put forth requirements which
                        according to the Turks recall too well the capitulatory regime; Mr. Grew the
                        American representative has requested new instructions from his Government.
                        The Turks have as a result postponed their departure from Lausanne. In case
                        the Americans should maintain their requirements the Turks have intimated a
                        possible postponement of the negotiations and their later resumption at
                        Constantinople.”</p>
                </quote>
                <p>Repeated to Constantinople.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
